                        <p
                            class="mx-auto mt-7 max-w-2xl text-pretty text-lg leading-8 text-white/68 sm:text-xl"
                        >
                            Forecast, prioritize, automate, and close with a
                            workspace that feels fast, focused, and built for
                            teams that move like pros.
                        </p>

                        <div
                            class="mt-9 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-3 sm:flex-row"
